    "For instance, combining video, audio, and text stimuli can offer a more comprehensive and nuanced understanding of learners' cognitive processes and behaviors.",
    "Additionally, using multimodal stimuli can help address the limitations of using a single type of stimuli and enhance the ecological validity of the study by better replicating real-world learning environments.",
